{"tid":143251,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 賴 慰 玲 昇 華 做 「 母 子 」","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T04:04:19.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93bbed97c2b7a53ca5465098e95a5aa8b391bcb2","tid":143251,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"吳業坤與賴慰玲在劇集《迷》中飾演傳媒新鮮人林家榮及萬子瑜，在追求理想及公義的理念下漸生情愫，但二人卻明言現實中撻唔着，感情已昇華至「母子」，認真搞笑！<br />\n<br />\n吳業坤（坤哥）與賴慰玲（Winki）雖在《迷》中成為情侶，但現實中的二人更似冤家，經常互窒，Winki一邊讚坤哥可愛，一邊踢爆他並非偽毒：「坤哥是堅毒，他很矛盾，時而很有自信，時而很自卑，為人複雜得像中毒般。不過，我們一定傳不到緋聞，因為已經昇華到母子關係，他叫我『阿媽』呢！」坤哥續說：「我一開始便講明不會拿她電話，到現在也沒有，只以微信溝通。況且她演戲已是『老江湖』，所以我們將這份愛昇華至母子。」<br />\n<br />\n二人能夠如此篤定做「母子」，一來是因為Winki已有穩定男友，二來她已明言坤哥不是她杯茶：「有些人只可以做朋友，我們可以好好傾，一起行街吃東西，就是不過電。」坤哥隨即不忿氣笑指要「撬牆腳」，Winki再發揮「毒舌」本色：「你試試吧！看看你有多少功架？我也不知你的自信從哪裏來？哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://toronto.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2017/03/enp05p01020317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoronto.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2017%2F03%2Fenp05p01020317.jpg&h=5a7995e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4e70fa30d3a74ee560c4ffca14077e4a4a7a7ef","tid":143251,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a69f19ed444cc8dc6d5e2547ee659fe472507be","tid":143251,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494de3920eda3a61a90767e9ca6398f2d0a6111d","tid":143251,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"賴慰玲無比坤哥食喇，mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3297e0c718de0f94107e2eadbb9e964ccb84c34","tid":143251,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賴慰玲<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要</span></span>比坤哥食喇，mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"65a135eb3eaa2ad0a91e917f63882defc199cbb2","tid":143251,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:16:01.000Z","msg":"死開啦坤狗"},{"pid":"4c3f8b9cf5d8abff7b79d275a58e47a7faaae177","tid":143251,"uid":56926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"咁係咪會亂倫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9687c9bdb1dd65a50c84e2b253819ab1aef5e5b1","tid":143251,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"坤狗全盛時期可以借幾多女藝人上位"}]}